Informatics as a separate subject and cross-curricular topic. Informatics in different age groups in Estonia and abroad. Learning materials. Test systems. Questions about informatics. E-learning. Learning objects. Repository. Didactics of informaticsObjectives/eesmärkid:  Student obtains an overview of the place of informatics (as separate subject and cross-curricular topic) in education.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After completing the course, the student will be able to: *describe teaching and learning informatics in different formats, age groups and school types in Estonia and abroad; *find, analyze, choose and adapt existing learning materials for students; *create learning materials for different lesson stages on the topic of informatics; *choose proper  teaching and learning methods for different age groups on the topic of informatics.
